subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Mike Helton, Nascar’s president, said it was “highly likely” the five-time champion Jimmie Johnson’s team would be penalized after the season-opening Daytona 500 on Feb. 26.
